== 反响 ==
电影中的言辞在当时被视为出格，使[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]市长和警务处长非常反感<ref name="Shaul2">{{cite journal|url=http://www.michiganhistorymagazine.com/features/discmich/anatomy.pdf|last1=Shaul|first1=Richard D.|title=Anatomy of a Murder|publisher=Michigan History|date=November–December 2001|page=89|format=PDF|archiveurl=https://wayback.archive-it.org/418/20061220154411/http://www.michiganhistorymagazine.com/features/discmich/anatomy.pdf|accessdate=2011-12-07|archivedate=2006-12-20|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。因此，该片在这个[[天主教|天主教]]影响深重的城市短暂遭禁<ref name="time.com">{{cite journal|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,869178,00.html|title=Cinema: The New Pictures, July 13, 1959|journal=[[Time_(magazine)|Time Magazine]]|date=1959-07-13|access-date=2016-01-28|archive-date=2013-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130827155938/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,869178,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。导演兼制片人普雷明格在伊利诺伊州联邦法院提出异议后，市长的决定被撤销了，影片得以放映。法庭认为该片中的语言在影片的上下文中是真实合理的<ref>{{cite book|title=The Face on the Cutting Room Floor|url=https://archive.org/details/faceoncuttingr00schu|first=Murray|last=Schumach|publisher=[[William_Morrow_and_Company|William Morrow and Company]]|year=1964}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=8pQuAAAAIBAJ&sjid=OUgDAAAAIBAJ&pg=7156,1608730|title=Chicago Loses Bid to Censor Movie|work=[[The_Deseret_News|The Deseret News]]|date=1959-07-09|accessdate=2011-10-28|archive-date=2017-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517115339/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=8pQuAAAAIBAJ&sjid=OUgDAAAAIBAJ&pg=7156,1608730|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

这部电影在法律和教育界收到良好反响。1989年，[[美国律师协会|美国律师协会]]将其列为史上最佳12部庭审电影之一，评价道：“该片真正的亮点是它展现了合理辩护是如何在一个困难案例中发展的。有多少庭审电影敢花那么多时间拍律师最常做（但最不喜欢做）的事——搜集资料？<ref>{{cite journal |last= Verrone |first= Patric M. |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=SpLZT79-g5IC&pg=PA96&lpg=PA96 |title= The 12 Best Trial Movies |journal= [[American_Bar_Association_Journal|ABA Journal]] |date= November 1989 |volume= 75 |issue= 11 |pages= 96–100 |issn= 0747-0088 |access-date= 2015-06-10 |via= [[Google_Books|Google Books]] |archive-date= 2015-09-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150904093529/https://books.google.com/books?id=SpLZT79-g5IC&pg=PA96&lpg=PA96 |dead-url= no }}</ref>”该片也在[[法学院|法学院]]中被用作教学片例，因为它涵盖了美国刑事制度中（被告角度）一场审讯的基本流程，从会见委托人到庭上的交叉质询等。

该片在[[爛番茄|烂番茄网站]]上获得了100%的新鲜度，42位影评人打出的平均分为8.6/10<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/anatomy_of_a_murder|title=Anatomy of a Murder|work=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2013-07-14|archive-date=2010-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100521050216/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/anatomy_of_a_murder/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

